 - Operators {{in}}, {{divby}}: {{FilterFunctions}}, mention that empty list means "just try"
 - $compute with read: {{ComputeSupported}} on entity set
 - $expand for stream properties and media resources:Â {{ExpandRestrictions/StreamsExpandable}}
 - /$query segment:Â {{QuerySegmentSupported}}

